entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: The rumors are true. The manager of the White Thranta Shipping company is going beyond Jabba's mandate of smuggling and monitoring space traffic around Tatooine. They are involved in medical research on sapient creatures. Jabba does not know this, and he must not find out. This gives you the opportunity to appease Jabba and betray him at the same time.
entries.journal_entry_description: Reimos has uncovered data which implicates the White Thranta Shipping company in some unethical medical experimentation. He has asked you to enter the complex and access a medical system that is on a closed network. Once inside the system extract the data he seeks and return to him.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Reimos feels something is up at the White Thranta Shipping offices and has you to investigate. Check into their computer system and return with information about their medical activities.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Reimos with the computer data.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Good Work! You have completed the Hidden Agenda quest.
